id§NOT_1499076262_7499511°datum§07.07.2017°DatumE§2017-07-07-00-00-00_NOT_1499076262_7499511°quelle§persistent°name§Mnogo: Installation einer Mongosearch Version in Vagrant°kategorien§.software.mnogosearch°info§°text§<br/>-----<br/><h1>2017 in Ubuntu Playbox07</h1><p>&gt;login als vagrant &nbsp;</p><p>sudo apt-get update</p><p>sudo apt-get install mysql-client-5.5 mysql-server-5.5 libmysqlclient-dev</p><p>mkdir -p /win/c/asmus/ablage/tmp;&nbsp;cd /win/c/asmus/ablage/tmp;</p><p>sudo tar&nbsp;<span style="background-color: #eeeeee; color: #222266; font-family: monospace; font-size: medium;">-zxf</span>&nbsp;/win/c/asmus/software-archive/mnogosearch-3.3.15.tar.gz</p><p>cd&nbsp;/win/c/asmus/ablage/tmp/mnogosearch-3.3.15;&nbsp;</p><p>sudo ./configure --with-mysql --with-openssl;</p><p>sudo make;&nbsp;sudo make install;</p><p>sudo mysql --user=root --password=root;</p><p><span style="color: #993366;">mysql&gt;</span>create database mnogo33_kbr;</p><p><span style="color: #993366;">mysql&gt;</span>exit</p><p>cd /usr/local/mnogosearch/etc</p><p><span style="color: #993366;">vagrant @ workbox : [1] /usr/local/mnogosearch/etc</span></p><p>mkdir -p /win/c/asmus/vhosts/mnogosearch/cgi/</p><p>sudo ln -s /win/c/asmus/vhosts/mnogosearch.localhost/conf/mnogo33_kbr.conf mnogo33_kbr.conf;</p><p>sudo ln -s /win/c/asmus/vhosts/mnogosearch.localhost/conf/searchxml_kbr.htm searchxml_kbr.htm;&nbsp;</p><p><span style="color: #800080;">DBAddr mysql://root:root@localhost/mnogo33_kbr/?socket=/var/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock&amp;dbmode=blob&amp;trackquery=yes</span></p><p>sudo cp langmap.conf-dist langmap.conf; sudo cp stopwords.conf-dist stopwords.conf;</p><p>sudo /usr/local/mnogosearch/sbin/indexer --create mnogo33_kbr.conf;</p><p>sudo /usr/local/mnogosearch/sbin/indexer -v 2 -a -c 30 -N 1 /usr/local/mnogosearch/etc/mnogo33_kbr.conf;</p><p>sudo /usr/local/mnogosearch/sbin/indexer -Eblob &nbsp;/usr/local/mnogosearch/etc/mnogo33_kbr.conf;</p><p>sudo /usr/local/mnogosearch/sbin/indexer -S /usr/local/mnogosearch/etc/mnogo33_kbr.conf;</p><p>sudo cp /usr/local/mnogosearch/bin/search.cgi /win/c/asmus/vhosts/mnogosearch.localhost/cgi-bin/searchxml_kbr.cgi;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h1>Alt - vor 2017:</h1><p>1 LUCID Box mit&nbsp;</p><p>php5</p><p>apache</p><p>mysqlserver</p><p>mysql client, mysqldev-lib</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>vagrant up</p><p>mnogo-tar unzip+entpacken</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Package configure</p><p>im mnogo dir als root: .</p><p>DBs: 2xnoyes</p><p>alles default, ausser: SSL: yes, Pfad: /usr/lib/ssl &nbsp;(find / -name ssl 2&gt;/dev/null)</p><p>erzeugt install.options datei, die editiert und nochmal aufgerufen werden kann</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>apt-get install make ## get make pkg</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>make</p><p>make install</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>database: http://localhost:9001/mysqladmin/&nbsp;</p><p>create database mnogodb:</p><p>mnogo:mnogo &nbsp;mnogodb</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>weiter mit http://www.mnogosearch.org/doc33/msearch-installing.html 5.)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>indexer.conf, search.htm:&nbsp;</p><p>DBAddr &nbsp;mysql://mnogo:mnogo@localhost/mnogodb/?dbmode=blob</p><p>create DB Tables: ./indexer -Ecreate</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>do the rest of the installation</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>°date§9.10.2015°files§°art§PC.Einrichtung PC.Installation